       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=Woody%20Hearn%20Interview&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Finterviews%2Farticle_19.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
